<>*3#8
       Chinese Egg Fried Rice.*2@1
       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@2
            Ingredients.@4
            ============@3       
12oz long grained rice
4oz mushrooms sliced
4 spring onions
4oz bean sprouts
4oz frozen peas
1 can bamboo shoots
2 tablespoons of soya sauce
3 eggs@1 (beaten)@3
a little oil for cooking.@7

           Method.@1
           ------@5
Wash  the  rice   under  running  cold
water.  Transfer the rice into a bowl,
cover  with cold water and  leave  for
30  minutes.  Drain the rice  and  put
into  a  pot,  add water and bring  to
the  boil,  cover tightly then  simmer
for  20  minutes @1  (  do  not stir!).





@5Remove  the  pot  from  the  heat  and
leave  to cool for 20 minutes,   cover
the pot with clingfilm and put in  the
fridge to chill for 2/3 hours.   Slice
the  mushrooms,cut the  spring  onions
diagonally  into 1 inch  pieces,   cut
the  bamboo  shoots   into  matchstick
size pieces.  Heat the oil in a frying
pan or wok to a high heat,add all  the
vegetables   and   stir  fry  for  2/3
minutes,  add the soya sauce and  cook
slightly   add   the   rice   to   the
vegetables  and cook  for  2  minutes,
pour  in  the beaten egg and stir  fry
for  2/3  minutes until the eggs  have
scrambled  and   the  rice  is  heated
through. Serve!@7


          Authors note.@1
          ~~~~~~~~~~~~

The  secret of perfect fried  rice  is
in  the   preparation,    follow  this
recipe  and you should find your  rice
is  as  good as that you buy  in  your
local takeaway!

